### Design System: "Mission Control"

The Academy Portal uses a distinct "Mission Control" design language - professional yet gamified, inspired by sports analytics dashboards and aviation control panels.

#### 1. Page Structure

**Hero Header Pattern (ALL pages must have this):**
```jsx
<div className="animate-fade-in pt-4 pb-12">
  {/* Hero Header - Mission Control Style */}
  <div className="mb-12 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start lg:items-end gap-6 pb-8 border-b-2 border-charcoal-100">
    <div>
      {/* Biometric Status Indicator */}
      <div className="mb-4">
        <BiometricStatusIndicator state={state} statusMessage={statusMessage} />
      </div>

      {/* Main Title - Large, Bold, Split Lines */}
      <h1 className="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-black text-charcoal-900 mb-4 tracking-tight leading-none">
        First Line<br />
        <span style={{ color: theme.pulseColor }}>Second Line</span>
      </h1>

      {/* Motivational Quote with Biometric-colored border */}
      <p className="text-charcoal-500 text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-heading italic border-l-2 pl-4 mt-6"
        style={{ borderColor: theme.pulseColor }}>
        &ldquo;Contextual motivational quote&rdquo;
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Score Cards - Right Side */}
    <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      {/* Primary Metric Card */}
      <div
        className="relative border-2 rounded-2xl p-6 bg-white shadow-elevation-md min-w-[140px]"
        style={{ borderColor: theme.pulseColor }}
      >
        <div
          className="text-5xl font-heading font-black leading-none tracking-tighter mb-1"
          style={{ color: theme.pulseColor }}
        >
          {value}<span className="text-xl align-top">%</span>
        </div>
        <div className="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-500 font-bold font-body">
          Metric Label
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Main Content Below */}
</div>
```

---

#### 2. Color Strategy (Biometric-Responsive)

**The Academy uses a LIGHT background with DARK accents (opposite of marketing site):**
- Page background: `bg-cream` or `bg-ivory` (set in AcademyLayout)
- Cards/Containers: `bg-white` with `border-2 border-charcoal-100`
- Text: `text-charcoal-900` (primary), `text-charcoal-500` (secondary)
- Shadows: `shadow-elevation-sm`, `shadow-elevation-md`, `shadow-elevation-lg`

**Biometric State Colors (dynamic, from useBiometric hook):**
| State | pulseColor | Meaning |
|-------|------------|---------|
| ember | `#EF4444` (red) | Needs encouragement, low engagement |
| neutral | `#3B82F6` (blue) | Steady state, normal activity |
| ascent | `#22C55E` (green) | Building momentum, active |
| apex | `#F59E0B` (gold) | Peak performance, top tier |

**How to use biometric colors:**
```jsx
const { state, theme, statusMessage } = useBiometric();

// theme provides: pulseColor, gradientFrom, gradientTo
<div style={{ borderColor: theme.pulseColor }}>
<div style={{ background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}, ${theme.gradientTo})` }}>
```

**Gamification Colors (static):**
- XP/Gold: `text-gold-600`, `bg-gold-100`
- Success/Complete: `text-forest-600`, `bg-forest-100`
- Warning: `text-amber-600`, `bg-amber-100`
- Info: `text-blue-600`, `bg-blue-100`

---

#### 3. Typography System

**Font Families:**
- `font-heading` - Display/titles (bold, impactful)
- `font-body` - Body text, labels, descriptions

**Title Hierarchy:**
- Page titles: `text-5xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-black`
- Section titles: `text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold`
- Card titles: `text-lg font-heading font-bold`
- Labels: `text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold font-body`

**Label Pattern (used extensively):**
```jsx
<div className="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-400 mb-1 font-body">
  Label Text
</div>
```

---

#### 4. Component Patterns

**Score/Stat Card:**
```jsx
<div className="border-2 border-charcoal-200 rounded-2xl p-4 bg-white shadow-elevation-sm">
  <div className="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-400 mb-1 font-body">
    Label
  </div>
  <div className="flex items-baseline gap-1">
    <span className="text-2xl font-heading font-black text-gold-600">
      {value}
    </span>
    <span className="text-xs text-charcoal-400 font-body">unit</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Progress Card with Accent:**
```jsx
<div className="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-charcoal-100 shadow-elevation-sm overflow-hidden">
  {/* Top accent bar */}
  <div className="h-1" style={{ background: `linear-gradient(90deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}, ${theme.gradientTo})` }} />
  <div className="p-6">
    {/* Content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

**Icon Container:**
```jsx
<div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-forest-100 flex items-center justify-center">
  <Icon size={18} className="text-forest-600" />
</div>
// Or with biometric gradient:
<div
  className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center"
  style={{ background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}20, ${theme.gradientTo}10)` }}
>
```

**CTA Button:**
```jsx
<button className="w-full group flex items-center justify-between p-6 bg-charcoal-900 text-white rounded-2xl shadow-elevation-md hover:shadow-elevation-lg transition-all duration-300">
  <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
    <div
      className="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center"
      style={{ background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}, ${theme.gradientTo})` }}
    >
      <Icon size={24} className="text-white" />
    </div>
    <div className="text-left">
      <div className="font-heading font-bold text-lg">Button Text</div>
      <div className="text-charcoal-400 text-sm font-body">Subtitle</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ArrowRight className="text-charcoal-400 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:text-white transition-all" />
</button>
```

