#### 6. Animation Classes

Available in globals.css:
- `animate-fade-in` - Fade in on mount
- `animate-slide-up` - Slide up with fade
- `animate-pulse` - Gentle pulse (for status indicators)

---

### STRICT NO-GO LIST

**DO NOT USE:**
- Dark backgrounds (reserve for marketing site)
- Full-screen heroes with scroll-flip (reserve for marketing)
- `rounded-full` on large elements
- Emojis anywhere
- Generic fonts
- `bg-charcoal-900` as page background
- Marketing-style gradients on backgrounds

**DO USE:**
- Light backgrounds (`bg-cream`, `bg-ivory`, `bg-white`)
- Mission Control header pattern
- Biometric-responsive colors via `useBiometric()`
- Score cards with prominent metrics
- `font-heading` for titles, `font-body` for text
- `shadow-elevation-*` for depth
- `rounded-2xl` for cards
- Lucide icons

