### Page-Specific Guidelines

| Page | Primary Focus | Key Metrics |
|------|---------------|-------------|
| /academy/portal | Welcome, motivation | Readiness Score, Rank, Streak |
| /academy/dashboard | Progress overview | Biometric %, Module Progress, XP |
| /academy/modules | Learning path | Completed/Total, Current Module |
| /academy/identity | Profile building | Skills Count, Profile Completeness |
| /academy/blueprint | Career roadmap | Milestones, Target Role |
| /academy/dojo | Interview practice | Belt Rank, Sessions, Confidence |
| /academy/assistant | AI pair programming | Active Threads, Messages |
| /academy/studio | Portfolio creation | Projects, Media Items |
| /academy/notifications | Alerts & updates | Unread Count, Total |
| /academy/profile | User settings | Streak, XP, Achievements |

